<subSubSection id="C3166561FFBCB516FF398748FD0F55F9" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB336EAFFBCB516FF398748FED55500" blockId="55.[189,303,267,293]" box="[189,303,267,293]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<heading id="D0FB8186FFBCB516FF398748FED55500" bold="true" box="[189,303,267,293]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B978EAF8FFBCB516FF398748FED55500" bold="true" box="[189,303,267,293]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB336EAFFBCB516FF39877AFD5855BF" blockId="55.[189,1399,313,410]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
This genus is erected to include 
<taxonomicName id="4C0C4D69FFBCB516FDC38779FCE35576" authorityName="Dietrich &amp; Magalhães &amp; Takiya" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Evans" baseAuthorityYear="1959" box="[583,793,313,339]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Plerujassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="appendiculatus">
<emphasis id="B978EAF8FFBCB516FDC38779FCE35576" box="[583,793,313,339]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">P. appendiculatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, described in 
<taxonomicName id="4C0C4D69FFBCB516FC42877AFBB65576" authorityName="Evans" authorityYear="1953" box="[966,1100,313,339]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Platyjassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B978EAF8FFBCB516FC42877AFBB65576" box="[966,1100,313,339]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Platyjassus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9D4B1BFFBCB516FBF98779FAE65571" author="Evans J. W." box="[1149,1308,313,340]" firstAuthor="Evans" journalOrPublisher="Memoires de l'Institut scientifique de Madagascar Tananarive (E" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" pagination="481 - 507" part="11" refId="ref49021" refString="Evans J. W. 1959. Quelques nouveaux Cicadellidae (Homopteres) de Madagascar. Memoires de l'Institut scientifique de Madagascar Tananarive (E) 11: 481 - 507." title="Quelques nouveaux Cicadellidae (Homopteres) de Madagascar" type="journal article" year="1959">Evans (1959)</bibRefCitation>
and an additional new species. It differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C0C4D69FFBCB516FDFF871EFCFB5552" authorityName="Evans" authorityYear="1953" box="[635,769,349,375]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Platyjassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B978EAF8FFBCB516FDFF871EFCFB5552" box="[635,769,349,375]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Platyjassus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in having transverse striations anteriorly on the crown and forewing venation densely reticulate.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB336EAFFBCB516FF398782FD0F55F9" blockId="55.[189,757,449,476]" box="[189,757,449,476]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis id="B978EAF8FFBCB516FF398782FD6F55FE" bold="true" box="[189,661,449,476]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
Key to species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0C4D69FFBCB516FE108782FDDA55F9" authority="Dietrich &amp; Magalhães &amp; Takiya, 2020" authorityName="Dietrich &amp; Magalhães &amp; Takiya" authorityYear="2020" box="[404,544,449,476]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Plerujassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B978EAF8FFBCB516FE108782FDDA55F9" bold="true" box="[404,544,449,476]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Plerujassus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A24B5783FFBCB516FDAC8782FD6F55FE" box="[552,661,449,475]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" rank="genus">gen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
(males)
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
